response.overview: The stunt team for the Star Trek: Section 31 film, which includes stunt coordinators and performers like Sebastian Buitrago, Shara Kim, and Daniel Lavigne. This team works with actor Michelle Yeoh, who performs many of her own action sequences, to create the film's fight choreography. The stunts are a key part of the film, which follows an all-star "misfit" crew working for the amoral secret organization, Section 31.
response.title: Section 31 Stunt Squad
